<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Zach Williams,, Bryan Fowler,, Jonathan Smith</author>
<title>Tirildim</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yillar davomida yuk ostida edim
 Sindim, majrux boldim tashvishlardan
 Marxamatingdan uzokda edim men
 Lekin Sen yul kursatding

[P1]
   Adashgandim men
   Sen yonimda eding
   Ojiz edim men
   Sen kuzlarim eding
   Ezilgan paytimda
   Sen nafasim eding
   Umid berding, ishonch berding menga

[C1]
   Men tirildim Senda
   Gunoxdan kutkarildim
   Xudo sevging ila
   Olovdan tortib olding
   Kayta tirildim

[V2]
 O, inoyatingni kura olaman
 Sening yulingdan yuraman men
 Zanjirlarimni uzib
 Xalos etding meni
 Umid berding, ishonch berding menga

[C2]
   Men tirildim Senda
   Gunoxdan kutkarildim
   Xudo sevging ila
   Olovdan tortib olding
   Kayta tirildim

[B1]
   Sen Kalkonim
   Sen Panoxim
   Sen ila men tirildim</lyrics>
</song>